  <brief_title>Open Surgery Versus Corticosteroid Injections in Treatment of Trigger Finger</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Surgery Versus Ultrasound Guided Local Corticosteroid Injections in Treatment of Trigger Finger - a Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
